    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Venture Into the Darkness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face your fears and survive as many floors of this cursed place as you can. Gain blessings to improve your capabilities, including passive buffs and active items to help you against the hordes. But watch out, if your batteries run out, you won't know what's coming next...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Blessings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find over 30+ different blessings that aid you in your struggle against the darkness. Gain a new blessing every time you complete a floor, and try to see how far you can go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293460/extras/443f6116e5be7bef6dbb1cb7481fc5e7.poster.avif?t=1731346755\" width=800 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293460/extras/443f6116e5be7bef6dbb1cb7481fc5e7.webm?t=1731346755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293460/extras/443f6116e5be7bef6dbb1cb7481fc5e7.mp4?t=1731346755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep Moving</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters you find in your journey have many weaknesses to learn and exploit, perhaps it's best to not always try to fight them head on. Avoid them and keep going, and try to search for ammo and health packs along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293460/extras/3b49dbe5a1eef4330f32b891ac451cc5.poster.avif?t=1731346755\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293460/extras/3b49dbe5a1eef4330f32b891ac451cc5.webm?t=1731346755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293460/extras/3b49dbe5a1eef4330f32b891ac451cc5.mp4?t=1731346755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
